563
00:13:18,865 --> 00:13:19,899
Yo-A-Jeong hay

564
00:13:19,899 --> 00:13:20,867
Tteokbokki!

565
00:13:20,867 --> 00:13:22,368
Dạo này có cái gì 'Du-Jjon-Ku' ấy

566
