571
00:13:29,876 --> 00:13:30,777
Hả!

572
00:13:30,777 --> 00:13:31,344
(Ông chú này làm sao đây)
Sao?

573
00:13:31,344 --> 00:13:32,845
Sao thế?

574
00:13:32,845 --> 00:13:33,579
